N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 7904.1 - Purpose and scope

State Regulations

This Part establishes procedures for appeals from
assignment orders, denial orders, and general distribution orders issued
pursuant to Parts 7901, 7902 and 7903 of this subchapter. Notes
